long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Github Pull request explorer

Browser extension that enhances to explore Github pull-request.

Feature 
- Sign-in with Github token
- Search pull-request by the filter
- Display the detail of pull-request on the pop-over
